      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，五个参与者。我确认一下顺序：Cloud Scheduler在最左边触发，API作为协调中心，OSCN是外部数据源，Database和Cloud Storage作为双存储落点？",
      "elements_involved": [
